hand_follow_hmi package:
compile with: rosmake hand_follow_hmi
run with: rosrun hand_follow_hmi hand_follow_hmi

Code for performing (crude) J'*dp based motion control of right arm to move
a hand frame (on palm of right hand) to coincide with a published point goal.

Compatible with demo HMI program "point_cloud_HMI"

Motion is slow and does not plan around collisions, but demonstrates initial integration with sensor-driven motion control
